description: 1-11/16" (Dia.) Premier Adjustable Rail & Stile Bit - Shaker

Optional double sided door cutter for the New Premier Adjustable Rail & Stile Shaker Style router bit system 99-762. Used with 99-762 New Premier Rail & Stile bits allows for double profile doors with variable thicknesses and long tenons. Perfect matching profile on all doors because it's the same set of router bits. Bits feature Freud's Perma-Shield coating that reduces heat and pitch build up along with rust, and Freud's TiCo Hi-Density Carbide to maximize bit life and material finish. Matches the Saker Style profile on the 99-760 rail & stile set.
